					z-index: -1;
					height: 100%;
					object-fit: fill;
					transition: 0.4s ease-in-out;
				}
			}

			.text {
				grid-column-end: 2;
				text-align: right;
				height: auto;
				margin-top: auto;
				margin-bottom: auto;
